      "GOAL_VPH_PARALLEL": "Venture Proving Holon (VPH) is a separate parallel subsystem with bounded capabilities and no direct promotion authority.",
      "GOAL_THREE_SOURCE_INTAKE": "Intake is explicitly three-source: DEFECT + INTENT + DRIFT. Two-source intake is non-compliant.",
      "GOAL_FAC_AUTHORITY": "FAC remains sole promotion authority; VPH/SIAR may propose and route but cannot merge or promote.",
      "GOAL_AAT_BIZ": "AAT-BIZ is a mandatory Stage-5 extension for strategy-critical or policy-classified work sourced from venture signals.",
      "GOAL_STRATEGY_COUPLING": "VPHI outputs must map to strategy evidence and support MSC-03, MSC-05, and MSC-06 progression without narrative-only gates.",
      "GOAL_MACHINE_CHECKABLE": "Every major VPHI objective must have baseline, quantitative target, boundary ID/time authority, owner locus, transition predicate, and evidence path.",
      "GOAL_ANTI_GOODHART": "Every optimized KPI must have independent countermetrics and fail-closed acceptance semantics.",
      "GOAL_EVIDENCE_FIRST": "No signal, route, or promotion claim is authoritative without signed receipts and replayable evidence bindings.",
      "GOAL_FAIL_CLOSED": "Unknown, stale, missing, parse-error, schema-invalid, or signature-invalid states are automatic deny outcomes.",
      "GOAL_DOMINANCE_ORDER": "Constraint precedence is non-negotiable: containment/security > verification/correctness > liveness/progress.",
      "GOAL_TIME_AUTHORITY": "Normative time logic uses HTF boundary/time-envelope authority; wall-clock is display-only.",
      "GOAL_SCALE_ENVELOPE": "Design must remain admissible under globally distributed multi-exabyte to zettabyte evidence and coordination envelopes.",
      "AEP_01": "Physics-first admissibility is mandatory; conventional execution anxiety cannot downscope goals.",
      "AEP_02": "Only physical, information-theoretic, computability, causality, biological, or explicit APM2 invariant limits can block proposals.",
      "AEP_03": "Novel engineering is required; analogies without mechanism-level contracts are invalid.",
      "AEP_04": "Compounding closure is mandatory: failure must strengthen verifiers/contracts/policies/primitives.",
      "AEP_05": "Bounded search discipline is mandatory: budgets, stop conditions, and escalation paths for every exploration.",
      "AEP_06": "Digest-first, typed, canonical, low-variety interfaces across holonic boundaries are mandatory.",
      "AEP_07": "Anti-Goodhart posture is mandatory: KPI + countermetric + independent oversight channel triplet.",
      "AEP_08": "Recursive semantic stability is mandatory: depth-bounded admissibility and composition-preserving interfaces.",
      "NOVELTY_METHOD": "Generate at least three divergent refinement tracks: (A) maximum ambition under physics, (B) maximum precision/testability, (C) maximum compounding velocity; synthesize dominant output.",
      "MECHANIZATION_RULE": "Every refinement claim must include mechanism, typed contract, threat mode addressed, measurable predicate, and evidence artifact path.",
      "OUTPUT_CONTRACT": "Deliver goal-coverage matrix, blocker/major/minor gap report, unified diffs, per-hunk rationale, physics feasibility ledger, AAT-BIZ coupling ledger, and fast experiments."
